<article class="row hentry post-265066 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-2020-election tag-bernie-sanders tag-climate-crisis tag-democrats tag-donald-trump tag-elizabeth-warren tag-neoliberalism tag-noam-chomsky section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-elections" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-trump-is-trying-to-exploit-tension-with-iran-for-2020/" title="Noam Chomsky: Trump Is Trying to Exploit Tension With Iran for 2020">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0718-pompeo-trump-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="President Trump talks with Secretary of State Mike Pompeo during a cabinet meeting at the White House, July 16, 2019, in Washington, D.C." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0718-pompeo-trump-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0718-pompeo-trump-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0718-pompeo-trump-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0718-pompeo-trump-1200x900.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/interview/' rel='category' class='interview'>Interview</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/war-and-peace/' rel='section' class='war-and-peace' style='color: #63164c;'>War &amp; Peace</a>
</div>
</div>
